extracted_info.microstructure: equiaxed grains with low-angle subgrain boundaries inside the grains and coarse intermetallic particles at grain boundaries
extracted_info.processing method: HIP'd for 2 h at 1400 °C and 207 MPa, annealed in a flowing argon furnace at 1400 °C for 6 h followed by a furnace cool to room temperature with the initial cooling rate of 20 °C/min
